               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18370814-name-1174" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18370814-name-1174" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18370814-name-1174" type="surname" value="STEVENSON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18370814-name-1174" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES STEVENSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I am in the service of William Edmund Champion, a linen-draper, at No. 93, High-street, Shadwell—we sell shoes. On the evening of the 2nd of August these shoes were hanging inside the door, with the label on them—I heard the bar that goes round the window rattle—I looked through the window, and saw the prisoner going past with a large black bag, twisting the mouth of it round—I went and missed one row of the shoes—I went after him and another—I went in front of them, and said, "Halloo"—I said he had got some shoes—he said he had not—I took the bag and found the shoes.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. PHILLIPS</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Were the shoes outside? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> No, inside the door—I saw no one take them down—the other one got away—the prisoner said the other one gave him the bag to carry.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18370814-name-1175" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18370814-name-1175" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18370814-name-1175" type="surname" value="PORTCH"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18370814-name-1175" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES PORTCH</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable K</hi> 91.) I took the prisoner into custody in Mr. Champion's shop—I said it was a pity you took such a quantity—he said it was done, and could not be undone.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
